21 for the Compact Privilege expires.
22 b. If the Licensee terminates the Qualifying License through
23 which the Licensee applied for the Compact Privilege before its
24 scheduled expiration, and the Licensee has a Qualifying License in
25 another Participating State, the Licensee shall inform the
26 Commission that it is changing to that Participating State the
27 Participating State through which it applies for a Compact
28 Privilege and pay to the Commission any Compact Privilege fee
29 required by Commission Rule.
